00:02:04.550 --> 00:02:07.790
that means when we're making figure A,

00:02:07.790 --> 00:02:09.990
if we look at the
corresponding side on figure B,

00:02:09.990 --> 00:02:12.640
so we have this side on figure B.

00:02:12.640 --> 00:02:16.260
It looks like it corresponds
